#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/gds.rst:244
msgid "POSIX fallback"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/gds.rst:246
msgid ""
"In some cases, libcufile implements its own internal POSIX fallback "
"without `GdsBackend` being aware. In others, an error such as "
"`RuntimeError: cuFileHandleRegister failed (cuFile err=5030, cuda_err=0)`"
" may be throwned. Thus, backend can be configured to fallback to its own "
"POSIX implementation when the usage of the GDS APIs is not successful."
msgstr ""

